-Exactly.

1446
01:03:43,319 --> 01:03:44,278
I said this earlier.

1447
01:03:44,362 --> 01:03:46,447
"I've never had a partner,
and I've never danced."

1448
01:03:46,531 --> 01:03:50,451
-"So how can I do partner dancing?"
-But you had to do both.

1449
01:03:50,535 --> 01:03:52,245
-"One at a time, please."
-Seriously.

1450
01:03:52,328 --> 01:03:55,414
The dance moves involved
holding hands and spinning.

1451
01:03:55,498 --> 01:03:57,834
I couldn't get a hold of myself

1452
01:03:57,917 --> 01:04:00,002
because data was pouring in
left and right.

1453
01:04:00,086 --> 01:04:01,420
-I bet it was overwhelming.
-I was a mess.

1454
01:04:01,504 --> 01:04:03,339
Oh, I honestly had fun.

1455
01:04:03,422 --> 01:04:04,882
-Really?
-It wasn't bad.

1456
01:04:04,966 --> 01:04:06,968
It was just a new experience.

1457
01:04:11,055 --> 01:04:12,723
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-What now?</i>

1458
01:04:12,807 --> 01:04:13,808
<i>-What?</i>
<i>-There she comes.</i>

1459
01:04:14,684 --> 01:04:16,227
-Is someone else coming?
-What?

1460
01:04:18,479 --> 01:04:19,397
<i>What?</i>

1461
01:04:20,815 --> 01:04:22,108
-Who is it?
-Another game changer?

1462
01:04:22,191 --> 01:04:24,694
Two game changers?

1463
01:04:24,777 --> 01:04:25,820
<i>What's going on?</i>

1464
01:04:29,740 --> 01:04:30,575
Someone's here.

1465
01:04:33,911 --> 01:04:35,580
-Hello.
-Hello.

1466
01:04:37,540 --> 01:04:40,209
<i>It was totally unexpected.</i>

1467
01:04:40,293 --> 01:04:42,086
I was taken aback.

1468
01:04:42,169 --> 01:04:45,965
I just thought,
"We keep getting pretty ladies here."

1469
01:04:46,048 --> 01:04:46,883
Wow.

1470
01:04:46,966 --> 01:04:48,217
Gosh, Seung-hyun.

1471
01:04:48,301 --> 01:04:51,345
-He just…
-He just finds every woman pretty.

1472
01:04:52,013 --> 01:04:54,557
It looks like
the highlight of this season is

1473
01:04:54,640 --> 01:04:57,852
watching Seung-hyun's dating show joyride.

1474
01:04:57,935 --> 01:04:59,270
Exactly. Come on.

1475
01:04:59,353 --> 01:05:01,314
-"We're getting so many beauties."
-Seriously.

1476
01:05:01,397 --> 01:05:02,231
"Wow."

1477
01:05:02,315 --> 01:05:04,650
-"Wow, she's pretty."
-I think…

1478
01:05:04,734 --> 01:05:06,360
-I think that's the highlight.
-Seriously.

1479
01:05:07,361 --> 01:05:09,780
<i>She was dressed up in black.</i>

1480
01:05:09,864 --> 01:05:12,325
<i>She looked very stylish.</i>

1481
01:05:12,408 --> 01:05:14,368
<i>She was graceful and pretty.</i>

1482
01:05:14,452 --> 01:05:18,080
So it made me wonder
why she's an eternal single.

1483
01:05:20,499 --> 01:05:22,043
<i>Honestly, I was a bit upset.</i>

1484
01:05:22,126 --> 01:05:24,629
After all, a new female participant meant

1485
01:05:24,712 --> 01:05:26,505
there'd be a new male participant as well.

1486
01:05:26,589 --> 01:05:27,632
That's all I could think about.

1487
01:05:27,715 --> 01:05:29,008
It was fun.

1488
01:05:29,967 --> 01:05:32,345
While holding each other's hands…

1489
01:05:35,806 --> 01:05:37,725
<i>A new participant is called</i>
<i>a "game changer."</i>

1490
01:05:37,808 --> 01:05:39,977
<i>So what kind of stunner</i>
<i>will they bring in?</i>

1491
01:05:43,189 --> 01:05:46,150
<i>We got a new man yesterday,</i>
<i>and another one today.</i>

1492
01:05:46,233 --> 01:05:49,236
<i>Every day is full</i>
<i>of hardships and ordeals.</i>

1493
01:05:49,862 --> 01:05:51,238
"You need to do better!"

1494
01:05:52,657 --> 01:05:54,158
-We had fun as well.
-True!

1495
01:05:58,579 --> 01:05:59,580
Hello.

1496
01:07:08,190 --> 01:07:10,192
Subtitle translation by: Dongjoo Park
